oday.Still, living in the U.S., it is a  striking fact that government regu=
lation here is often aimed less at=C2=A0restricting=C2=A0fossil fuel use an=
d more at protecting=C2=A0it. =E2=80=9COne day soon it will be illegal to i=
nvest in oil, so let=E2=80=99s get ready,=E2=80=9D is the ESG thesis, but i=
n Texas=C2=A0it has recently become illegal=C2=A0not=C2=A0to invest in oil.=
